<div class="container">

<div class = "description">
  <div class="grid grid-pad">
    <div class="col-1-3">
      <div class="content">
        <p class = "beerme">Beer Me</p>
        <h4 class = "descript">Beer Me uses your geolocation to pinpoint the nearest places for you to find a beer, and helps get you there ASAP.</h4>
        <div class="button login"><a href="#">Log In</a></div>
        <div class="button signup"><a href="">Sign Up</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<h1>How It Works</h1>

<div class="grid grid-pad">

  <div class="col-1-3">
    <section>
      <i class="fa fa-users fa-4x"></i>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="col-1-3">
    <section>
      <i class="fa fa-map-marker fa-4x"></i>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="col-1-3">
    <section>
      <i class="fa fa-beer fa-4x"></i>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="col-1-3">
    <section>
      <h3>Log In or Sign Up</h3>
      <p>Log in, or create a secure account. BeerMe will use your geolocation to find the nearest venues for you to purchase a beer.</p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="col-1-3">
    <section>
      <h3>Browse Venues</h3>
      <p>You are provided with the pertinent information on each venue. Compare venues' ranks and see their current popularity. Use BeerMe's directions feature to map your route to a chosen locale.</p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="col-1-3">
    <section>
      <h3>Save Your Favorites</h3>
      <p>Save your favorite venues or store the places you want to visit in the future. They'll be there anytime you revisit the site. Cheers!</p>
    </section>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="addedContent grid grid-pad">
  <!-- Sign In Form -->
<div class="col-1-1 forms">
  <h3 class="form-title-si">Sign In</h3>
  <form class="pure-form locateuser" action = "/login" method = "post">
    <fieldset>

        <input class="loginem" type="email" placeholder="Email" name="email">
        <input class="loginpw" type="password" placeholder="Password" name="password">

        <button type="submit" class="pure-button button-error">Sign in</button>
    </fieldset>
  </form>

  <!-- Sign Up Form -->
    <h3 class="form-title-su">Sign Up</h3>
    <form class="pure-form pure-form-aligned locatenewuser" action = "/users" method = "post">
    <fieldset>
      <div class="pure-control-group">
        <label for="name">First Name</label>
        <input id="name" class="createfn" type="text" placeholder="First name" name="user[first_name]">
      </div>

      <div class="pure-control-group">
        <label for="name">Last Name</label>
        <input id="name" class="createln" type="text" placeholder="Last name" name="user[last_name]">
      </div>

      <div class="pure-control-group">
        <label for="email">Email Address</label>
        <input id="email" class="createm" type="email" placeholder="Email Address" name="user[email]">
      </div>

      <div class="pure-control-group">
        <label for="password">Password</label>
        <input id="password" class="createpw" type="password" placeholder="Password" name="user[password]">
      </div>

      <div class="pure-controls">
        <button type="submit" class="pure-button button-error">Sign Up</button>
      </div>
    </fieldset>
  </form>
 </div>
</div>

